{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 2088485, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 406499, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "肯定任盈盈啊。对于小师妹只有敬，对于任盈盈才是亲近和无拘无束。", "timestamp": 1626574226, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2088487, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 406499, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "任你令狐再冲，也逃不过盈盈一握", "timestamp": 1626574262, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2088490, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 406499, "reply_to": 2088487, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 最后一句我想歪了", "timestamp": 1626574332, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2088492, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 406499, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "笑傲江湖最后，令狐冲和任盈盈去华山看到那只马猴，感叹他本来自由放纵，现在也被牵系在心爱之人身上，也如一只马猴", "timestamp": 1626574383, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2088493, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 406499, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "所以，没有绝对自由，哪怕武功天下第一，江湖总是在拘束你", "timestamp": 1626574422, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2088494, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 406499, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "我是马猴（顿悟", "timestamp": 1626574440, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2088498, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 406499, "reply_to": 2088487, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 可是原书写的令狐冲对任盈盈的心理活动倒大多是恩情", "timestamp": 1626574502, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2088501, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 406499, "reply_to": 2088494, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 马猴绑着劳德诺", "timestamp": 1626574524, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2088504, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 406499, "reply_to": 2088498, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 上少林寺救是恩，但恒山上被绑在一起时是情", "timestamp": 1626574571, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2088512, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 406499, "reply_to": 2088498, "tag": null, "text": "任盈盈可贵就可贵在她不完全依附令狐冲，有自己独立的人格。在少林寺观看令狐冲和师傅比剑时，想着:你若是心里无我，我就算站在你前面提醒你，也是无趣", "timestamp": 1626574690, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2088513, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 406499, "reply_to": 2088487, "tag": null, "text": "令狐冲几次在任盈盈面前对岳灵珊含情脉脉什么心理", "timestamp": 1626574690, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2088515, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 406499, "reply_to": 2088513, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 初恋，他的白月光", "timestamp": 1626574715, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2088519, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 406499, "reply_to": 2088513, "tag": null, "text": "令狐冲多情但不滥情，他当然忘不了小师妹，但也是由衷祝福林平之和师妹成婚，觉得自己不适合。", "timestamp": 1626574797, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2088533, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 406499, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "金庸不擅长写男女情，往往是呆板了无生趣，但最后一部笑傲江湖是写得最好的", "timestamp": 1626574981, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2088544, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 406499, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "女性读者路过，其实我觉得这段感情里任盈盈亏了，圣女独美不好么", "timestamp": 1626575124, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2088550, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 406499, "reply_to": 2088513, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 金庸的女性太有男性附庸了", "timestamp": 1626575226, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2088563, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 406499, "reply_to": 2088513, "tag": null, "text": "女人生存的全部意义似乎是把自己弄的完美可爱，然后等一个侠客路过，把她绑定，沉浸在对感情的执着中。", "timestamp": 1626575365, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2088564, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 406499, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "最不自由的令狐冲", "timestamp": 1626575384, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2088568, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 406499, "reply_to": 2088563, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 对，所以任盈盈的独立意识是最强的", "timestamp": 1626575409, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2088571, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 406499, "reply_to": 2088544, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 问世间情为何物", "timestamp": 1626575434, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2088573, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 406499, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "任盈盈在令狐冲之前没有感情经历吗，绿竹巷与令狐冲相处几日就值得坚定托付终身吗", "timestamp": 1626575533, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2088574, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 406499, "reply_to": 2088544, "tag": null, "text": "而且盈盈的聪明让她在感情中始终占主导权", "timestamp": 1626575541, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2088580, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 406499, "reply_to": 2088573, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 绿竹巷算是因曲结缘，真正加深感情是因为令狐冲护送她下山，她求少林救令狐，令狐冲上少林救她", "timestamp": 1626575639, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2088582, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 406499, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "为什么小说女主都是美貌若仙明艳不可方物", "timestamp": 1626575673, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2088583, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 406499, "reply_to": 2088582, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 苦笑", "timestamp": 1626575714, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2088585, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 406499, "reply_to": 2088573, "tag": null, "text": "任盈盈在黑木崖只能见到阿谀奉承之辈，没见过一个率真而又身遭重伤饱受猜疑，却不改侠士风流的男子", "timestamp": 1626575747, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2088587, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 406499, "reply_to": 2088582, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 因为武侠小说的受众就是男性为主吧", "timestamp": 1626575799, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2088598, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 406499, "reply_to": 2088587, "tag": null, "text": "侠士风流在我看来也就是一种既定荣辱观。真君子伪君子也无甚区别", "timestamp": 1626575939, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2088603, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 406499, "reply_to": 2088598, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 真伪之辨，在于心境。倘若满口仁义，内里作恶，本就违背圣人之道", "timestamp": 1626576041, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2088606, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 406499, "reply_to": 2088598, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 有侠士风流得绝世神功得美人相伴，无侠士风流终为人唾弃", "timestamp": 1626576070, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2088607, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 406499, "reply_to": 2088606, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 这就是圣人之道", "timestamp": 1626576116, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2088608, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 406499, "reply_to": 2088603, "tag": null, "text": "不愿受世俗矫饰，尚质朴天然", "timestamp": 1626576117, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2088615, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 406499, "reply_to": 2088607, "tag": null, "text": "你说的不对，侠士之道自古存于中华文化，匡扶正义，重诺轻死", "timestamp": 1626576187, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2088621, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 406499, "reply_to": 2088607, "tag": null, "text": "至于神功，美人，都是外在一番奇遇，吸引市井读者而已", "timestamp": 1626576238, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2088627, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 406499, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "洞主是女生吧，对金庸小说感兴趣？", "timestamp": 1626576305, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2088629, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 406499, "reply_to": 2088627, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 洞主是男生", "timestamp": 1626576370, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2088639, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 406499, "reply_to": 2088629, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 感觉你心思很细腻", "timestamp": 1626576461, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2088646, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 406499, "reply_to": 2088627, "tag": null, "text": "“不愿受世俗矫饰，尚质朴天然”是天资如此？令狐冲自幼岳不群扶养没有抛弃自然本性全因天资高？其他人难窥伺道是因天资不够？", "timestamp": 1626576532, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2088652, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 406499, "reply_to": 2088646, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 这就要跳出小说，考究作者本意了。金庸塑造令狐冲，是想表达一种政治理想", "timestamp": 1626576629, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2088654, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 406499, "reply_to": 2088646, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 作者设定，不可深究", "timestamp": 1626576666, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2088678, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 406499, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 对金庸小说这些设定感觉总有种不平之气，正邪分明；滥杀无罪；主次鲜明。感觉更像是一种舞台剧，虽然画面人物鲜明", "timestamp": 1626577088, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2088680, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 406499, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "所以金庸写的终究是流行小说，而非传世巨著", "timestamp": 1626577100, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2088687, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 406499, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "就是一眼看到底情节人物......，格局不够", "timestamp": 1626577228, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2088700, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 406499, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "射雕三部曲里，女性都是由守护者变成被守护者", "timestamp": 1626577381, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2088705, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 406499, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "说到底，金庸写的武侠是写给男性读者看的，男性凝视的意味很浓。其实金庸的武侠小说也可视为那个时代的“爽文”，男主角能练成绝世神功，能抱得美人归，能施展拳脚实现自己的抱负。这和小白爽文代表《斗罗大陆》中，唐三历经磨难娶回小舞，得封海神有什么本质区别吗", "timestamp": 1626577496, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2088735, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 406499, "reply_to": 2088705, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 比之爽文还有些政治隐喻政治理想吧", "timestamp": 1626577787, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2088743, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 406499, "reply_to": 2088735, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 硬要说的话…是有的。不过我能读出的就是金庸对“侠义”的理解。其实也不是什么很深的东西。", "timestamp": 1626577881, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2088750, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 406499, "reply_to": 2088743, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 嗯同意。武侠小说以侠为背景但对“侠”本身却没有更深探讨", "timestamp": 1626578039, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2089120, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 406499, "reply_to": 2088750, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 你要说探讨，我觉得是借“侠以武犯禁”探讨“儒以文乱法”。所描述之武功高低，颇似对文章高低的评判标准。由此而看，是个人之力之智，与法与势斗之悲剧。观其结尾，应势者昌，逆势者隐，格局未必便甚低。", "timestamp": 1626583976, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2091932, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 406499, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "任盈盈不是金庸追不到谢梦 怒而写出来的完美女性吗？ 各方面都是女神，但是就喜欢令狐冲这个傻小子", "timestamp": 1626615539, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2092341, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 406499, "reply_to": 2091932, "tag": null, "text": "Re Grace: 令狐冲对岳灵珊对任盈盈好像都没有真正主动过。都是被甩被追。不用主动真好😀充分满足男性读者心理需求", "timestamp": 1626619804, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2092390, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 406499, "reply_to": 2091932, "tag": null, "text": "尚朴天然还是最喜欢潇湘夜雨，暗下杀手可以死不承认，和岳女比剑可以自甘落败，形势不利可以容忍退让，还会装死活命", "timestamp": 1626620190, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2092414, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 406499, "reply_to": 2092390, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 几乎可说是没有骨气没有义气不顾声誉没有荣辱观", "timestamp": 1626620421, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 8, "pid": 406499, "reply": 53, "tag": null, "text": "令狐冲在岳灵珊面前呆头呆脑生怕说错话，在任盈盈面前聪明活泼油嘴滑舌。所以哪一种是爱？", "timestamp": 1626574060, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1626620420, "url": "", "vote": {}}}